description: This is a market on predicting the statements made by Trump at his upcoming rally in Georgia.

markets.description:
Donald Trump has scheduled a town hall on October 28 in Atlanta, Georgia (see: https://event.donaldjtrump.com/events/president-donald-j-trump-to-hold-a-rally-in-atlanta-ga).

Any usage of the term regardless of context will count toward the resolution of this market.

If this candidate does not appear at this event, or if the event is otherwise cancelled or delayed beyond October 28, this market will resolve to "No".

The resolution source will be the video of the speech.
